Under which two circumstances would an administrator reset the web content event log?
(Choose two.)
A. As a pre-migration step during migration planning
B. As a post-migration step during migration after syndication
C. To troubleshoot syndication problems such as items on the syndicator not being sent
D. If the contents of the repository were modified by using the membe rf ixe r task without
specifying the update flag
E. If the contents of the repository were modified through an external mechanism such as a
JCR import or other custom application
Answer: C,E
